        "content": "Web search results for query: \"Xcode 26.3 AI agent launch Claude OpenAI February 2026\"\n\nI'll perform a web search for that query.\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"​从“助手”进化为“代工”！苹果发布 Xcode 26.3：原生集成 Claude 与 ChatGPT\",\"url\":\"https://m.itbear.com.cn/html/2026-02/1170381.html\"},{\"title\":\"​从“助手”进化为“代工”苹果发布 Xcode 26.3：原生集成 Claude 与 ChatGPT\",\"url\":\"https://m.chinaz.com/ainews/25724.shtml\"},{\"title\":\"苹果Xcode 26.3上线：AI编程从“给建议”到“写代码”\",\"url\":\"https://finance.sina.cn/stock/jdts/2026-02-27/detail-inhpfhtu0916177.d.html\"},{\"title\":\"苹果 Xcode 26.3 上线:AI 编程从“给建议”到“写代码”\",\"url\":\"https://mparticle.uc.cn/article_org.html?uc_param_str=frdnsnpfvecpntnwprdssskt#!wm_cid=738431511491002368!!wm_id=1d2d859a7da24a0187a2256ca80b9f80\"},{\"title\":\"苹果 Xcode 26.3 正式上线：AI 编程从“给建议”迈步“写代码”\",\"url\":\"https://wap.ithome.com/html/924065.htm\"},{\"title\":\"苹果 Xcode 26.3 正式上线：AI 编程从“给建议”迈步“写代码”\",\"url\":\"https://tech.sina.cn/2026-02-27/detail-inhpfhtq6776548.d.html\"},{\"title\":\"Xcode 26.3 扩展支持编程智能体，可接入 Claude Agent、Codex 等\",\"url\":\"https://www.infoq.cn/article/39BuXj6WpGFqPERk4X9x\"},{\"title\":\"苹果Xcode 26.3版本集成智能体编程支持功能\",\"url\":\"https://news.sina.cn/ai/2026-02-10/detail-inhmihnh4610195.d.html?fromsinago=1,1712\"},{\"title\":\"Xcode 迈入Agent 时代-- 肘子的Swift 周报#122 - 稀土掘金\",\"url\":\"https://juejin.cn/post/7604694326517940275\"},{\"title\":\"Xcode 迈入Agent 时代-- 肘子的Swift 周报#122 - Fatbobman's Blog\",\"url\":\"https://fatbobman.com/zh/weekly/issue-122/\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, I found information about Xcode 26.3 with AI agent capabilities. Here's a summary of the key findings:\n\n## **Xcode 26.3 Launch - February 2026**\n\n### **Core Announcement**\nApple officially released **Xcode 26.3 on February 27, 2026**, marking a significant shift in AI-assisted programming. The update represents a major evolution from AI as a \"copilot\" providing suggestions to AI as an \"agent\" capable of autonomous task execution.\n\n### **Key Features**\n\n**1. Autonomous AI Coding Agents**\n- AI agents can deeply understand project structure\n- autonomously break down complex development goals\n- execute modification logic across multiple files\n- directly interact with developer projects\n- analyze file structure, modify underlying files, and execute complex workflows across entire projects\n\n**2. Native Integration**\n- **OpenAI Codex** - natively integrated\n- **Anthropic Claude** - natively integrated\n- Developers can flexibly switch between models based on needs\n- Built-in **Swift 6.2.3** and latest SDK\n\n**3. Model Context Protocol (MCP)**\n- Open standard allowing third-party AI providers to seamlessly connect to Xcode\n- Enables use of any MCP-compatible agent or tool\n- No need for complex third-party plugins\n- Can be enabled via: `xcrun mcpbridge`\n\n**4. Fine-Grained Permission Control System**\n- AI agents must obtain explicit developer authorization before accessing or modifying core project resources\n- Prevents AI from unconditionally accessing sensitive code\n- Balances development efficiency with code security\n- \"Licensed operation\" mechanism effectively prevents potential security risks\n\n### **Significance**\nThis release标志着苹果在 AI 编程领域迈出了跨越性的一步，让 AI 直接参与到开发流程中，全方位协助和提升开发者生产力。AI 不再仅仅是提供代码建议的\"副驾驶\"，而是成为了能够自主执行任务的\"智能体\"。\n\n*Note: The search results appear to be from Chinese tech news sites reporting on this announcement, all dated February 27, 2026.*\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."
      }
    ]
